            <h2 class="headline">
                <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2017/climate/what-is-climate-change.html" data-tracking-index="9" data-rref="">Climate Change Is Complex. We’ve Got Answers to Your Questions.</a>
            </h2>
            <p class="summary">We know. Global warming is daunting. So here’s a place to start: 17 often-asked questions with some straightforward answers.</p>
            <p class="byline">
                <span class="freshness"><time data-utc-timestamp="1505793916" datetime="1505793916"></time></span>
                                <span class="divider"></span>
                                <span class="author" itemprop="author">By JUSTIN GILLIS</span>
            </p>
        </div>
    </article>
</li>
                </ol>
        </div>
                        </section>
    
    
